07:09.100 --> 07:11.800
chief. I can go to the morgue
with you.

07:11.800 --> 07:13.200
We'll sort this out.

07:13.300 --> 07:15.900
Oh, chief, um,
this, uh,

07:16.000 --> 07:17.900
fax didn't quite make it through.

07:18.000 --> 07:19.300
Um, i called the service guy.

07:19.400 --> 07:21.700
He's supposed to be here
tomorrow morning, 11:00 a.m.

07:22.300 --> 07:23.900
Lieutenant tao, thank you.

07:24.000 --> 07:26.100
I'll find another fax machine
along the way.

07:30.400 --> 07:32.100
Gabriel came off suspension
friday night.

07:32.200 --> 07:33.700
Why don't you give him a call
to come in?

07:33.800 --> 07:35.700
But we'll be done with this
before he even gets here.

07:35.800 --> 07:37.600
Would you just do it, flynn?

07:38.200 --> 07:40.100
God, you're a pain in the ass.

07:47.800 --> 07:49.700
Let me guess...
natural causes?

07:49.800 --> 07:51.500
If we were guessing,

07:51.600 --> 07:54.500
i wouldn't be cutting the old guy open
and pulling out his intestines.

07:54.600 --> 07:56.000
I'd still be at brunch...

07:56.100 --> 07:59.100
with my friends,
having a mimosa.

08:00.000 --> 08:03.000
Well, dr. Morales, i'm so sorry
to interrupt your sunday,

08:03.100 --> 08:07.300
but it's important to establish that
mr. Kaplan here is <i>not</i> a homicide victim.

08:07.500 --> 08:09.900
Well, you better wipe off
your crystal ball, honey,

08:10.000 --> 08:12.300
because this guessing thing
isn't working for you.

08:12.400 --> 08:14.100
Mr. Kaplan <i>was</i> murdered?

08:14.400 --> 08:16.900
You see this nasty irritation
along the esophagus?

08:17.000 --> 08:19.500
Some hemorrhaging, too...
there and there,

08:19.600 --> 08:21.300
and the stomach was pretty torn up.

08:22.200 --> 08:23.000
Which means...

08:23.100 --> 08:25.500
violent vomiting before death.

08:27.300 --> 08:30.100
Even in advance of a tox screen,
i'd say poison.

08:31.400 --> 08:33.799
All the offices with
fax machines were closed, chief,

08:33.900 --> 08:36.000
- so no luck sending this.
- Oh, shoot.

08:36.100 --> 08:40.299
<i>But</i> i did dig up
six death certificates,

08:40.400 --> 08:42.900
one for each name
that the old man gave us.

08:43.000 --> 08:45.600
Now, they all died
within the last year.

08:45.700 --> 08:46.800
And get this...

08:46.900 --> 08:50.100
they all lived at a place
called the summer view senior living center.

08:50.200 --> 08:54.600
Now, while the certificates indicate that
they died of natural causes,

08:54.700 --> 08:56.700
they're all signed...

08:57.400 --> 08:59.200
by the same physician.

09:05.300 --> 09:09.300
All right, mr. Stiltskin,
i'm not ignoring you anymore.

09:12.000 --> 09:13.500
??

09:33.800 --> 09:36.200
- What are <i>you</i> doing here?
- You mean, in <i>my</i> office?

09:36.300 --> 09:37.800
Oh, sorry. Um...

09:37.900 --> 09:39.800
you're holding a delusional
old man in an interview room

09:39.900 --> 09:41.700
on a sunday afternoon...
yeah, i know that.

09:41.800 --> 09:44.200
You're wrapping that up, right,
sending everybody home until tomorrow?

09:44.300 --> 09:45.700
Uh, not exactly.

09:45.900 --> 09:48.100
Look, it's irritating, i know.

09:48.200 --> 09:49.100
But as it turns out,

09:49.200 --> 09:50.900
the dead guy actually <i>was</i> poisoned,

09:51.000 --> 09:54.000
which means that we have
six more potential victims.

09:54.200 --> 09:55.400
So, get the death certificates.

09:55.500 --> 09:57.100
- That'll have a cause of death.
- We did that.

09:57.200 --> 09:59.400
They all supposedly died
of natural causes.

09:59.500 --> 10:02.500
But each death certificate
was signed by the same doctor.

10:02.600 --> 10:05.000
And when a doctor signs off
on a death certificate...

10:05.100 --> 10:06.100
there's no autopsy.

10:06.200 --> 10:07.400
Oh, my god, brenda,

10:07.500 --> 10:10.100
tell me you didn't just fax orders
for the exhumation of six bodies.

10:10.200 --> 10:11.600
Okay, i didn't.

10:14.200 --> 10:17.300
I just faxed the offer.
I have the confirmation in my hand.

10:17.400 --> 10:20.000
Well, nothing has come through.
Can you just do it again?

10:20.200 --> 10:22.800
Gary says doris could
get another offer any minute.

10:23.700 --> 10:25.000
And gary doesn't lie.

10:25.100 --> 10:27.700
It's there...
in the machine.

10:27.800 --> 10:28.900
It's <i>not.</i>

10:29.400 --> 10:31.400
All right. I'll try and send it
again later.

10:32.000 --> 10:34.000
For heaven's sake!

10:38.000 --> 10:39.500
Oh, chief,
if you can believe it,

10:39.600 --> 10:41.800
six of the dead bodies were cremated.

10:44.000 --> 10:44.900
Track down the ashes.

10:45.000 --> 10:47.300
Any family members give you a problem,
get a warrant.

10:47.400 --> 10:50.300
Uh, lieutenant tao, are we
signed to search the nursing home?

10:50.400 --> 10:51.400
Uh, not quite.

10:51.500 --> 10:54.500
The judge wants us to specify
the room numbers we want to look at.

10:54.800 --> 10:56.100
Oh.

11:02.700 --> 11:03.800
Ohh!

11:13.000 --> 11:15.900
We have determined that
the six people you named

11:16.000 --> 11:17.800
are, in fact, deceased.

11:18.300 --> 11:22.100
And they all lived at the same
nursing home prior to their deaths.

11:22.200 --> 11:24.000
Congratulations, young lady.

11:24.100 --> 11:26.400
You're that much closer
to finding out who i am.

11:26.500 --> 11:28.800
And that much closer to
treating you like a murderer,

11:28.900 --> 11:30.700
which seems to be what you want!

11:31.700 --> 11:33.000
Now,

11:33.100 --> 11:36.600
i have a warrant to search
mr. Kaplan's room,

11:36.700 --> 11:40.000
- but i need a room number.
- 308.

11:41.700 --> 11:44.200
Might you have a room
at this facility, as well?

11:45.700 --> 11:47.500
Find out for yourself.

11:51.300 --> 11:53.100
Say "cheese."

11:57.200 --> 11:58.500
Thank you.

12:07.600 --> 12:08.400
- Oh!
- Oh! Hi.

12:08.500 --> 12:09.500
Sergeant gabriel!

12:10.800 --> 12:11.600
What are you doing here?

12:11.700 --> 12:13.400
I thought you weren't
coming back until tomorrow.

12:13.500 --> 12:15.700
L-i spoke to daniels,

12:15.800 --> 12:18.000
and she said the squad was on call,

12:18.100 --> 12:22.500
and my, uh, suspension was up friday.

12:22.900 --> 12:25.500
Uh, i think this fax came for you.

12:25.600 --> 12:27.400
Oh, shoot!

12:27.500 --> 12:29.300
I faxed myself.

12:29.400 --> 12:32.700
- Chief, nursing home awaits!
- Oh, yes, thank you.

12:32.800 --> 12:36.300
Um, i just need to...
send a fax.

12:37.700 --> 12:38.900
Oh, sergeant gabriel...

12:41.400 --> 12:46.000
uh, if you could,
please babysit the suspect while i'm gone.

12:47.500 --> 12:48.600
Thank you.

12:52.400 --> 12:54.900
And there's no need to beat
information out of this old man.

12:55.000 --> 12:56.900
He's been confessing all morning.

